正确选项：BCD

解释：

汽车以额定功率行驶时，即在其额定功率范围内工作 Cuando un vehículo se mueve a su potencia nominal, es decir, cuando trabajaa dentro de su rango de potencia nominal. During this time, the car is only capable of doing:

A. 匀速直线运动 (uniform linear motion) - 可以做uniform linear motion. It can move at a constant speed along a straight line;

C. 减速直线运动 (uniformly decelerating linear motion) - 可以做uniformly decelerating linear motion. It can slow down at a constant rate along a straight line;

不可能做：

B. 匀加速直线运动 (uniformly accelerating linear motion) - 不能做uniformly accelerating linear motion. As the car is working within its power rating, it cannot accelerate at a constant rate;

D. 匀速圆周运动 (uniform circular motion) - 不能做uniform circular motion. As the car is moving along a straight line, it cannot follow a circular path.

因此，选项 BCD 都是正确的选项。
